#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:76
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Szczegóły"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:78
msgid ""
"On any warehouse transfer (e.g. receipt, delivery order), add a product to a "
"package by clicking the :guilabel:`Details` link in "
"the :guilabel:`Operations` tab."
msgstr ""
"W dowolnym transferze magazynowym (np. przychód, zamówienie dostawy) dodaj "
"produkt do opakowania, klikając link :guilabel:`Szczegóły` w "
"zakładce :guilabel:`Operacje`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:None
msgid "Details link on the product line."
msgstr "Link Szczegóły w wierszu produktu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/package.rst:84
msgid ""
"Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` pop-up window for "
"the :guilabel:`Product`."
msgstr ""
"Spowoduje to otwarcie okna podręcznego :guilabel:`Operacje szczegółowe` "
