#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:70
msgid "Generate Sendcloud credentials"
msgstr "Wygeneruj dane uwierzytelniające Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:72
msgid ""
"In the Sendcloud account, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Integrations` in the menu on the right. Next, search for :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Native`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Na koncie Sendcloud przejdź do :menuselection:`Ustawienia --> Integracje` w "
"menu po prawej stronie. Następnie wyszukaj :guilabel:`Odoo Native`. Potem "
"kliknij :guilabel:`Połącz`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:75
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Connect`, the page redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud API` settings page, where the :guilabel:`Public and "
"Secret Keys` are produced. The next step is to name "
"the :guilabel:`Integration`. The naming convention is as follows: `Odoo "
"CompanyName`, with the user's company name replacing `CompanyName` (e.g. "
"`Odoo StealthyWood`)."
msgstr ""
"Po kliknięciu :guilabel:`Połącz` strona przekierowuje do strony "
"ustawień :guilabel:`Sendcloud API`, gdzie generowane są :guilabel:`Klucze "
"publiczny i tajny`. Kolejnym krokiem jest nazwanie :guilabel:`Integracji`. "
"Konwencja nazewnictwa jest następująca: `Odoo NazwaFirmy`, gdzie nazwa firmy "
"użytkownika zastępuje `NazwaFirmy` (np. `Odoo StealthyWood`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:80
msgid ""
"Then, check the box next to :guilabel:`Service Points` and select the "
"shipping services for this integration. After saving, the :guilabel:`Public "
"and Secret Keys` are generated."
msgstr ""
"Następnie zaznacz pole wyboru obok :guilabel:`Punkty obsługi` i wybierz "
"usługi wysyłkowe dla tej integracji. Po zapisaniu zostaną "
"wygenerowane :guilabel:`Klucze publiczny i tajny`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Configuring the Sendcloud integration and receiving the credentials."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurowanie integracji z Sendcloud i otrzymywanie danych "
"uwierzytelniających."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:90
msgid ""
"To ensure seamless Sendcloud integration with Odoo, :ref:`install <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` and :ref:`link <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` the Sendcloud shipping connector "
"to the Sendcloud account. Then, :ref:`configure Odoo fields <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, so Sendcloud can accurately "
"pull shipping data to generate labels."
msgstr ""
"Aby zapewnić bezproblemową integrację Sendcloud z Odoo, :ref:`zainstaluj "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` i :ref:`połącz <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` konektor wysyłki Sendcloud z "
"kontem Sendcloud. Następnie :ref:`skonfiguruj pola Odoo <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, aby Sendcloud mógł prawidłowo "
"pobierać dane wysyłkowe do generowania etykiet."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:98
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable pickup points on websites <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-pickups>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Włącz punkty odbioru na stronach internetowych <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-pickups>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:103
msgid "Install Sendcloud shipping module"
msgstr "Zainstaluj moduł wysyłki Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:105
msgid ""
"After the Sendcloud account is set up and configured, it's time to configure "
"the Odoo database. To get started, go to Odoo's :guilabel:`Apps` module, "
"search for the `Sendcloud Shipping` integration, and install it."
msgstr ""
"Po skonfigurowaniu konta Sendcloud nadszedł czas na skonfigurowanie bazy "
"danych Odoo. Aby rozpocząć, przejdź do modułu :guilabel:`Aplikacje` w Odoo, "
"wyszukaj integrację `Wysyłka Sendcloud` i zainstaluj ją."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Sendcloud Shipping module in the Odoo Apps module."
msgstr "Moduł Wysyłka Sendcloud w module Aplikacje Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:116
msgid "Sendcloud shipping connector configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracja konektora wysyłki Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping` module "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"The :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector` setting is found under "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` section."
msgstr ""
"Po zainstalowaniu aktywuj moduł :guilabel:`Wysyłka Sendcloud` "
"w :menuselection:`Magazynowanie --> Konfiguracja --> Ustawienia`. "
"Ustawienie :guilabel:`Konektor Sendcloud` znajduje się w "
"sekcji :guilabel:`Konektory wysyłkowe`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:122
msgid ""
"After activating the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector`, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Po aktywowaniu :guilabel:`Konektora Sendcloud` kliknij "
"link :guilabel:`Metody wysyłki Sendcloud` poniżej wyświetlonego konektora. "
"Po przejściu na stronę :guilabel:`Metody wysyłki` kliknij :guilabel:`Nowy`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Shipping "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
"Do :guilabel:`Metod wysyłki` można również przejść, "
"wybierając :menuselection:`Magazynowanie --> Konfiguracja --> Dostawa --> "
"Metody wysyłki`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:130
