msgstr ""
":ref:`Skonfiguruj metodę dostawy <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"delivery-method>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper.rst:65
msgid ""
":ref:`Activate production environment <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
