"Click the :guilabel:`Replenish` button on the top-left of the product page. "
"In the pop-up window, set the warehouse to the retail shop, (e.g. `Store`), "
"and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknij przycisk :guilabel:`Uzupełnij` w lewym górnym rogu strony produktu. "
"W oknie podręcznym ustaw magazyn na sklep detaliczny (np. `Store`) i "
"kliknij :guilabel:`Potwierdź`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:0
