#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/purchase_dashboard.rst:64
msgid "This KPI is impacted by purchases with future expected receipts."
msgstr ""
"Ten wskaźnik KPI jest zależny od zakupów z przyszłymi oczekiwanymi odbiorami."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/purchase_dashboard.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On time deliveries`: indicates the percentage of products "
