#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/advanced/purchase_dashboard.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`% On time deliveries by vendor`: shows the percentage of products "
"received on time, by vendor (based on expected arrival on purchase order "
